snippet.title: Super Chicken Catchers - PLAY AS THE RIDER
snippet.description:
This little guy jumps and glides in the air, be ready to drop bombs like crazy! Team up with your mount and combine your skills to claim the title!

Super Chicken Catchers is a video game developed by White Smoke Games

• Website: https://whitesmokegames.com
• Facebook: https://fb.com/superchickencatchers
• Twitter: https://twitter.com/SCC_Game
